description: Sun Splashed 2-Bed, 2-Bath w/Private Outdoor Spaces & Deeded Parking. Featuring soaring 9.5-ft ceilings, elegant crown molding, & oversized windows.The open-concept layout is anchored by a chef’s kitchen equipped w/top-of-the-line SS appliances, breakfast bar, & built-in wine fridge. Luxurious primary suite offers a peaceful retreat with custom walk-in closet, & spa-inspired en-suite bath complete w/rain shower. Second bedroom is equally versatile as a guest room, home office, or both. Enjoy year-round comfort w/central heating/cooling, & in-unit laundry. Step out onto your private balcony for morning coffee or unwind on the expansive private roof deck, plumbed for water, gas & offering stunning city & water views. Two deeded tandem pkg spaces & an enormous private basement storage room complete this home. Moments from shopping, dining, vibrant nightlife, grocery stores, Castle Island, & the newly remodeled Curley Community Center. Seller welcomes offers with requests for compensation.
